  "html": "<h1>Applies to</h1>\n  <ul>\n    <li>PCI DSS Requirement 3.1.b</li>\n  </ul>\n  <h1>What to Check For</h1>\n  <p>The information security policy should include provisions for data disposal.</p>\n  <h1>How to Check</h1>\n  <p>Check the information security policy to make sure that it includes provisions for data disposal.</p>\n  <h1>How to Fix</h1>\n  <p>Identify the method for disposing of data that is older than required by the data retention policy. Describe in detail the chosen method for data disposal and include the description in the information security policy.</p>\n  <h1>Related Items</h1>\n  <ul>\n    <li>\n      <p>\n        <a href=\"/article/40de7c85-0fdd-4894-a3a1-943d4316fb12\">Prepare the Data Retention and Disposal Policies</a>\n      </p>\n    </li>\n  </ul>"
